#  Banking Customer Analysis Dashboard | Python, SQL & Power BI

## Project Overview

This project focuses on analyzing banking customer data using Python, SQL, and Power BI to uncover valuable insights related to customer demographics, loans, deposits, occupations, banking relationships, and income segments.

The project follows a complete data analytics workflow starting from data extraction and cleaning in Python, followed by Exploratory Data Analysis (EDA), and finally building interactive Power BI dashboards to support data-driven business decisions.

---

##  Business Objective

Banks generate large amounts of customer and financial data every day. Understanding customer behavior, lending patterns, deposit trends, and banking relationships is crucial for improving customer engagement and business performance.

This project aims to transform raw banking data into meaningful insights through data analysis and visualization.

